    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S is a purist\u2019s configuration, powered by the 3.8L M97 flat-six engine paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical suite includes Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional turn-in and corner-exit traction. This example features a documented service history, including a recent borescope inspection and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the engine remains high-revving and leak-free with immediate throttle response. It is a mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the canyons.",
